01:00:55.360 --> 01:00:56.736
Anh sẽ đợi hai mẹ con.

01:01:06.204 --> 01:01:07.038
Ông xã.

01:01:11.417 --> 01:01:12.251
Cảm ơn anh.

01:01:31.062 --> 01:01:31.896
